corepack enable
pnpm install
pnpm approve-builds # press 'a'(select all) and then press 'enter'

* create .env.local and fill it *
pnpm dev

* open a new terminal *
npm i -g firebase-tools
firebase emulators:start --only auth,firestore,functions,storage

* if we added Cloud Functions update the script *

* open a new terminal *
cd search-service
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8081

* can open docs in the browser to see all of the endpoints *


